   = b^{−4}  
   = 1 / b^{4}

c)  c^{−8} · c^{−7}  
   = c^{(−8 − 7)}  
   = c^{−15}  
   = 1 / c^{15}

Final answers:  
a) a^5  
b) b^{−4}  (or 1/b^4)  
c) c^{−15} (or 1/c^{15})

